<main>
    <section class="services">
        <h1>Our Services</h1>

        <div class="service">
            <img src="adoption.png" alt="Service 1">
            <h2>Adopt</h2>
            <p>At Furry Rescue, we're passionate about bringing pets and people
            together. Our adoption process is designed to create lifelong bonds between loving
            families and deserving pets. We carefully match you with the perfect furry friend
            based on your lifestyle, preferences, and needs. Our dedicated team is here to guide
            you every step of the way, ensuring a smooth and joyful adoption journey.
            When you choose to adopt from us, you're not just giving a pet a home; you're
            gaining a loyal companion who will bring warmth and happiness to your life.
            Join us in making a difference—one paw at a time."</p>
            <a href="#">Learn More</a>
        </div>

        <div class="service">
            <img src="donate.png" alt="Service 1">
            <h2>Donate</h2>
            <p>
                At Furry Rescue, we rely on the generosity of kind-hearted individuals
                like you to support our mission of rescuing and caring for animals in need.
                Your donations play a crucial role in providing shelter, food, medical care,
                and love to the pets we serve. Whether you choose to make a one-time contribution
                or become a regular donor, your support helps us make tails wag and hearts smile.
                Together, we can create a brighter future for animals and give them the second chance
                they deserve. Your donation is not just a gift; it's a lifeline for our furry friends,
                bringing hope and happiness to their lives. Join us in making a positive impact and
                be a part of our journey to make the world a better place for animals."
            </p>
            <a href="#">Learn More</a>
        </div>

        <div class="service">
            <img src="Foster.png" alt="Service 3">
            <h2>Foster </h2>
            <p>
                Our foster care program at Furry Rescue is a lifeline
                for pets in need. By becoming a foster parent, you provide a temporary, loving
                home for animals awaiting their forever families. Fostering is a rewarding experience that allows you to make a direct impact on an animal's life. It's a chance to nurture, heal, and prepare them for a successful transition to a permanent home.

                As a foster parent, you'll receive all the necessary support, supplies, and
                guidance from our dedicated team. Whether it's a kitten needing socialization,
                a dog recovering from surgery, or a senior pet seeking companionship, your love
                and care make a world of difference. Fostering is a flexible commitment, and you'll have the opportunity to witness transformation and resilience in the pets you help.

                Join us in providing these animals with a safe haven, a loving environment,
                and the chance to thrive. Your role as a foster parent is not just a temporary
                arrangement; it's a vital stepping stone towards a brighter future for the pets
                we serve. Together, we're making tails wag and hearts smile, one foster home at
                a time.
            </p>
            <a href="#">Learn More</a>
        </div>



        <div class="service">
            <img src="volunteer.png" alt="Service 4">
            <h2>Volunteer</h2>
            <p>
                Join the heartwarming journey of making a difference in the
                lives of animals through our volunteer program at Furry Rescue. As a volunteer,
                you have the opportunity to be the compassionate hands and kind hearts that bring comfort,
                care, and hope to our furry friends.

                Our dedicated volunteers play a crucial role in supporting our mission.
                Whether you're helping with daily care routines, socializing animals, assisting with events,
                or lending your skills behind the scenes, your commitment makes a significant impact.
                Volunteering isn't just about donating your time; it's about being part of a community
                that shares a common love for animals.

                We welcome volunteers of all backgrounds and experience levels. No matter your skill set,
                there's a place for you here. By offering your time and expertise, you're contributing to
                the well-being of pets in need and helping us fulfill our promise to provide a brighter
                future for them.

                Become a part of our volunteer family, and experience the joy of knowing you're making tails
                wag and hearts smile. Together, we can create a world where every animal receives the love
                and care they deserve.
            </p>
            <a href="#">Learn More</a>
        </div>

    </section>
</main>


